f=Product/loom/operational/skill/loom-skill-routing.md · h1:loom Skill Routing Map=`a plan rests on beliefs ─► assumption-mapping (surface, score, rank riskiest-first) \· │ top assumption \· ▼ \· experiment-registry (QUERY: settled? stale? new?) ─settled─► cite verdict, don't re-run \· │ new/stale` · h1:loom Skill Routing Map=Non-leader: law (the Evidence Gate loom supplies experiment verdicts PMF reads) routing decide WHICH skill WHEN. Handoffs out: spec (test-first verdicts in/out; experiment evidence) metric (experiment-instrumentation, retention curves) (qualitative why, assumption evidence) price (revenue experiments; viability) marcus/vista (PMF verdict double-down/pivot; roadmap) proto/forge/scout (shared experiment adopt-reject patterns) anneal (overturned verdicts skill lessons). Precedence: query registry before running; criteria frozen before data; near-miss miss; PMF thresholds flagged rubric.